												<p class="travel-stories-single-post-date"><a href="https://stevenchu.com/blog/the-vanishing-point-the-new-male-silhouette/" title="Permalink to The Vanishing Point – The New Male Silhouette" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2008-06-08T02:46:12+00:00">June 8, 2008</time></a></p>

						<p class="travel-stories-single-post-author"> <a href="https://stevenchu.com/blog/author/stevenchu/" title="Posts by stevenchu" rel="author">stevenchu</a></p>
